{"word":"ἐκεῖθεν","slug":"ἐκεῖθεν","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἐϰεῖϑεν</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐκεῖ\">ἐκεῖ</a></el> + -<el>ϑεν</el> as point of origin] <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adv.\">adv.</a> ‘from that place’, <b>from there, thence <a href='B:470 4:21'>Mt 4:21</a>; <a href='B:480 6:1'>Mk 6:1</a>; <a href='B:490 9:4'>Lk 9:4</a>; <a href='B:500 4:43'>J 4:43</a>; <a href='B:510 13:4'>Ac 13:4</a>; <a href='B:730 22:2'>Rv 22:2</a>.</b> <el>οἱ <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐκεῖθεν\">ἐκεῖθεν</a></el> those from there <b><a href='B:490 16:26'>Lk 16:26</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a></b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐκεῖ\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐκείνης\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}